514
00:21:01.620 --> 00:21:03.620
Alright, bring it in. What are we?

515
00:21:03.620 --> 00:21:05.620
Normal size bugs.

516
00:21:05.620 --> 00:21:06.620
What do we do?

517
00:21:06.620 --> 00:21:09.620
Travel through an interdimensional game, wait a minute, we're letting tiny people.

518
00:21:09.620 --> 00:21:10.620
Why do we do it?

519
00:21:10.620 --> 00:21:11.620
To spread the cure for AIDS.

520
00:21:11.620 --> 00:21:15.620
Hey, Sarge, how do we know if these little people can understand us?

521
00:21:15.620 --> 00:21:17.620
I mean, do they even speak bugganese?

522
00:21:17.620 --> 00:21:18.620
Funny, Policky.

523
00:21:18.620 --> 00:21:20.620
That's why we say it very loud.

524
00:21:20.620 --> 00:21:23.620
Guys, you'll still be the same civilized bug on their side.

525
00:21:23.620 --> 00:21:27.620
It's not like interdimensional travel strips us of our clothes and makes us screaming monsters.

526
00:21:27.620 --> 00:21:29.620
Or maybe it does, impossible to know.

527
00:21:29.620 --> 00:21:31.620
Now get out of here.

528
00:21:34.620 --> 00:21:37.620
My clothes. Where'd they go?

529
00:21:51.620 --> 00:21:53.620
Did you get any of that?

